{
  "stem": "5970.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father had a collection of gold coins, which were sold bit by bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It lasted till actually, till 1944, when we were sent to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived on these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously, they paid very little for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We got a fraction what it was worth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at least there was some food in the house till the last minute.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I said, life was-- was different, all together-- restrictions, and different orders, and harassment all the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Radom, it was comparatively late.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Radom-- let me tell you a little bit about the town-- was an industrial city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jewish population, according to statistics, as far as I can remember, was 30,000 to 35,000 Jews in town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But during the first two years, that swelled to about 40,000, because there were a lot of people coming from other ghettos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were ghettos already established, and people were coming to-- to Radom thinking they could find work there easier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if you worked, you had a chance of staying in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you didn't have work, you were just rounded up and sent away to one of the death camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were a lot of-- we called them the foreigners-- from Lublin, from Lodz, from Krakow, from Warsaw-- who came to Radom during the first two years of-- of the war and the-- the places where they-- most of them worked.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was later on in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one was in a-- in a-- in another-- on the other side of town, called Glinice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was the second.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The big ghetto was in the old town, where we were-- where we were actually transferred there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
